This is destined to be a period of change but also of swift progress. Things will all just seem to fall together and you will not feel shackled to things like work or relationships. These sorts of things define you and might change often. You may find yourself jumping between careers or jobs, doing one thing for a while and then abandoning that for the next great adventure. Travel, free-spiritedness, and all manner of experimentation may well be part of the overall picture. Your actions will all be very liberating but be careful to avoid self harm. Drink in every possible experience. Travel. Learn. Experience everything you can. This is your time to suck the marrow out of life so have at it and catalogue every point on your journey. It's going to be interesting, to say the least.
